03:08.640 --> 03:09.960
Oh. Yeah.

03:16.720 --> 03:18.400
I thought it was here.
Maybe it's...

03:19.000 --> 03:20.160
Maybe it's in the back.

03:22.400 --> 03:23.560
Maybe I finished it.

03:25.200 --> 03:26.680
- Good news.
- What?

03:26.760 --> 03:28.960
