James.

04:00.560 --> 04:02.280
Well, this isn't creepy at all.

04:06.840 --> 04:10.240
<i>♪ You know, I'd sail the stormy seas ♪</i>

04:10.960 --> 04:14.040
<i>♪ </i><i>Just for you to notice me ♪</i>

04:15.560 --> 04:18.600
<i>♪ I'd fight a million wars ♪</i>

04:19.200 --> 04:22.600
