06:26.240 --> 06:27.440
Do you reckon those are real?

06:28.000 --> 06:29.000
I don't know.

06:35.320 --> 06:36.480
They're quite sharp.

06:36.560 --> 06:38.920
All right, Captain Safety, chill out.

06:40.920 --> 06:42.080
We should check on Bonnie.

06:42.640 --> 06:44.080
