to end up dead than married.

10:17.800 --> 10:18.800
Right.

10:19.160 --> 10:20.440
You can relax now.

10:20.960 --> 10:23.560
He's safety. He's solid.

10:24.480 --> 10:27.280
<i>Says the woman abandoned
by every man she's ever been with.</i>

10:27.360 --> 10:28.400
Look at him.

10:30.600 --> 10:31.600
I am.

10:34.640 --> 10:36.720
How do you feel?

10:37.080 --> 10:38.560
Exactly the same.

10:39.760 --> 10:41.320
You're a lucky girl.

10:50.280 --> 10:53.240
<i>I do.
I feel exactly the same.</i>

10:55.560 --> 10:56.560
<i>Shit.</i>

10:56.960 --> 11:03.040
<i>♪ Every heart finds delight ♪</i>

11:03.120 --> 11:08.080
<i>♪ In the chapel of dreams ♪</i>

11:08.160 --> 11:12.240
