14:49.840 --> 14:51.160
if that's what you want.

14:52.960 --> 14:53.960
Maybe.

14:54.280 --> 14:56.040
<i>I didn't know what that meant.</i>

15:05.720 --> 15:07.000
What happened to you...

15:08.520 --> 15:09.720
